<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Microsoft JhengHei", "PingFang TC", sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #c9a227;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #8b0000;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .header p {
      color: #666;
      margin: 10px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .info-label {
      width: 100px;
      color: #666;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .info-value {
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .amount {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #c9a227;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .note {
      background: #fffbeb;
      border: 1px solid #c9a227;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>佳里廣澤信仰宗教協會</h1>
    <p>捐款收據</p>
  </div>

  <p><%= @donation.donor_name %> 您好：</p>

  <p>感謝您對本協會的善心捐獻！您的功德將廣結善緣，庇佑平安。</p>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="info-row">
      <span class="info-label">收據編號</span>
      <span class="info-value"><%= @donation.receipt_number %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="info-row">
      <span class="info-label">捐款類型</span>
      <span class="info-value"><%= @donation.donation_type_name %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="info-row">
      <span class="info-label">捐款日期</span>
      <span class="info-value"><%= (@donation.paid_at || @donation.created_at).strftime("%Y年%m月%d日") %></span>
    </div>
    <% if @donation.prayer.present? %>
    <div class="info-row">
      <span class="info-label">祈福內容</span>
      <span class="info-value"><%= @donation.prayer %></span>
    </div>
    <% end %>

    <div class="amount">
      捐款金額：NT$ <%= number_with_delimiter(@donation.amount) %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="note">
    附件為您的捐款收據 PDF 檔案，請妥善保存。如有任何疑問，歡迎與我們聯繫。
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>功德無量，福慧雙修</p>
    <p>佳里廣澤信仰宗教協會 敬上</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
